Further information
Rishworth Aviation on behalf of our client Garuda Indonesia are now accepting applications from B777-300ER Type Rating Instructors (TRI) for the placement of B777-300ER Type Rating Instructors (TRI) on a 1 year contract with Garuda Indonesia based in Jakarta, Indonesia.
****SCREENINGS FOR 2014 - ONGOING!! APPLY TODAY!!!****
Contract Term: 1 Year
Location/Base: Jakarta, Indonesia
Ref: 959
Minimum Requirements:
5000+ Jet hours;
1000+ hours on type;
Valid ICAO licence with current B777-300 & TRI rating;
Valid Class 1 Medical Certificate;
3 take offs and landings on type within the last 90 days;
and ICAO level 4 English proficiency
Benefits:
3 weeks on / 1 week off, housing allowance will be provided, per diem allowances when on layover, access to travel privileges on Garuda's network and medical insurance is provided as part of your contract.
For more details and to fast track your application please APPLY NOW and register at www.rishworthaviation.com, once registered you will be able to view the full job description including pay. If you are registered already please login to your pilot portal.
Pilots who don't yet meet these experience requirements are invited to register and update their details at www.rishworthaviation.com. When your experience matches our position requirements, we will be able to notify you of positions which you qualify for, which may be of interest to you.
